f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db48449c8e0547815a6692420e58c41c8e071328","tid":910723,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:23:55.000Z","msg":"金澤要去, 名古屋無野玩既"},{"pid":"885a10aa7ea8159d11fbbe6614f0696bf531a3f0","tid":910723,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:26:27.000Z","msg":"衰d講句, 高山市好細, 12月呢d時間5點幾就收哂鋪, 同埋宮川朝市都好撚雞的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新穗高就早d去, 晏d 上到山頂淨係睇到霧, 最好住果邊附近d住宿<br />\n白川鄉 留3-5個鐘乜都夠<br />\n金澤反而可以睇一日, 好彩既話雪景既兼六園都幾靚, 金澤城都算唔錯<br />\n<br />\n其他你d行程我未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}